reviewText: I'veen seen this show originally in HBO, and i like it very much. The package is good enough for the price, the discs has been treated very well, inside has good pictures of the show, and the quality of the image and the sound are acceptable. Is a good stuff for fans, and the 1st. season has a good extras.
